description:
In Viviter's multiplayer mode, you can play "Chickempic" with up to 8 players, and we're adding the "Fly Me to the Moon" mini-game!
Right now, a lone astronaut is about to take off from the X Space Center to reach the moon!
It's a direct one-way flight to the lunar surface. Whether you can make it depends on your judgment!
While the button is pressed, the balloon will be filled with air and dreams! And when you release the button, the journey to the moon begins!!!
name: Additional mini-game "Fly Me to the Moon"
